channel.title: Kieran Harrison - There & Back (HYDRANS Remix) [Hardcore, Dubstep]
channel.description:
Kieran Harrison - There & Back (HYDRANS Remix) *headphones recommended*
[Click Here!](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/kieran-harrison-there-back) [or Here (my Soundcloud) ](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans)
My remix of @KieranHarrison's track There & Back from his Arkitek EP!
I just want to say thanks to Andrew for letting this happen! He was the winner of a remix contest I hosted so this is my way of saying thank you. Check him out here: [Kieran Harrison](https://soundcloud.com/kieranxharrison) Also, the original song is amazing! Check it out here: [Kieran Harrison - There & Back](https://soundcloud.com/kieranxharrison/there-back)
Let me know how it turned out! Any listens and likes are appreciated as well as feedback!
Thanks! ~ HYDRANS
[details="Side Note -"] Make sure to listen to the second drop, i'm really proud of that one! [/details]

item.dc:creator: anon86704580
item.description:
I like this a lot!! Intro is a bit repetitive to be honest. I guess I can’t say much, right? The first drop seems a bit… off to me. Idk why. But, the second drop? OMG!! SO GOOD!! Maybe not your best song in my opinion, but it’s still really good. So, that says something about you
